WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.440 --> 00:00:03.480
Tools for Change:

00:00:04.340 --> 00:00:06.380
Yoga for Peace,

00:00:06.380 --> 00:00:11.390
'Nadi Suddhi'. '

00:00:11.390 --> 00:00:12.860
Nadi Suddhi' means 'to

00:00:12.860 --> 00:00:17.320
purify the nadis.'


00:00:17.320 --> 00:00:18.920
When speaking of nadis, we will not be talking

00:00:18.920 --> 00:00:22.520
about all 72,000 of them,


00:00:22.520 --> 00:00:24.930
because
these 72,000 originate from

00:00:24.930 --> 00:00:27.180
only two
basic nadis: 'Ida

00:00:27.180 --> 00:00:29.980
' and 'Pingala.'


00:00:29.980 --> 00:00:32.750
36,000 extend from 'Pingala,' and

00:00:32.750 --> 00:00:36.930
another 36,000
extend from 'Ida.'

00:00:36.930 --> 00:00:40.970
This is human
energy physiology.

00:00:42.100 --> 00:00:44.510
Fundamentally, 'Nadi Suddhi' refers to purifying

00:00:44.510 --> 00:00:47.100
'Ida' and 'Pingala' so that the


00:00:47.100 --> 00:00:51.690
energy system can function in balance.


00:00:51.690 --> 00:00:55.970
Your breath and mental structure are
interconnected. Bringing

00:00:55.970 --> 00:00:58.310
balance to your thoughts is an


00:00:58.310 --> 00:01:01.700
 
important step you must take. If you wish to find balance in your

00:01:01.700 --> 00:01:05.030
activities, emotions, and
life outcomes, and if you

00:01:05.030 --> 00:01:06.940


00:01:06.940 --> 00:01:09.810
 
want to have influence over the lives of others,

00:01:09.810 --> 00:01:13.370
'Nadi Suddhi' will play a
significant role. To set the best conditions for

00:01:14.800 --> 00:01:23.200
properly learning this practice, I will
 
give you a few guidelines. Please

00:01:23.600 --> 00:01:28.522
turn off your mobile phone or put it on silent. Full

00:01:28.840 --> 00:01:35.250
stomach  This program is not suitable if you are in a state of intoxication or immediately after finishing a meal.


00:01:35.560 --> 00:01:41.400
Sit with your spine straight and comfortable.
Do not overlap your hands; keep your
palms facing upward.

00:01:41.880 --> 00:01:50.520
These conditions can increase your receptiveness and allow you to draw the
maximum benefit from the practice.


00:01:50.960 --> 00:01:56.280
This practice is very simple and safe, making it
easy to follow.

00:01:57.040 --> 00:02:04.240
Anyone 7 years of age or older
can learn and perform it.

00:02:05.232 --> 00:02:12.360
If you wear glasses, please
 
remove them and set them aside during the yoga practice. Let's look at

00:02:13.260 --> 00:02:16.320
how to do 'Nadi Suddhi'
together. Do

00:02:16.320 --> 00:02:18.720
not follow along yet.

00:02:18.720 --> 00:02:22.650
Fold your legs to
keep your spine comfortable and

00:02:22.650 --> 00:02:25.430
close your eyes.

00:02:25.430 --> 00:02:28.920
Loosely rest your left hand on the
center of your legs with your

00:02:28.920 --> 00:02:31.850
palm
facing upward.

00:02:31.850 --> 00:02:34.170
Use only your right hand.

00:02:34.170 --> 00:02:37.060
 
Use your thumb and ring finger, and fold your

00:02:37.060 --> 00:02:39.890
middle and index fingers. Straighten your


00:02:39.890 --> 00:02:42.600
ring and little fingers and


00:02:42.600 --> 00:02:45.380
 
bring the sides of your fingers together.

00:02:45.380 --> 00:02:48.670
Now, block your right nostril with your thumb and


00:02:48.670 --> 00:02:51.360
 
inhale to the left.

00:02:51.360 --> 00:02:56.470
Inhale completely and
exhale to the left. In a

00:02:56.470 --> 00:02:58.320
similar way,

00:02:58.320 --> 00:03:01.550
 
block your left nostril with your ring finger and inhale to

00:03:01.550 --> 00:03:06.620
the right,

00:03:06.620 --> 00:03:10.680
then exhale through the right nostril.


00:03:10.680 --> 00:03:14.110
Again, block the right and
open the left to inhale and exhale.

00:03:14.110 --> 00:03:19.040


00:03:19.040 --> 00:03:22.160
Continue doing this.

00:03:22.160 --> 00:03:25.310
Focus on your breath.  The most important thing

00:03:25.310 --> 00:03:28.770
when doing 'Nadi Shuddhi'


00:03:28.770 --> 00:03:32.800
 
is to fully inhale and fully exhale. Do it

00:03:32.800 --> 00:03:34.790
 
as slowly

00:03:34.790 --> 00:03:36.970
and
gently as you can. Do

00:03:36.970 --> 00:03:38.930
 


00:03:38.930 --> 00:03:41.560
 
not create different sounds while inhaling and exhaling. If you remember just one basic thing while

00:03:41.560 --> 00:03:43.490
doing this breathing,

00:03:43.490 --> 00:03:46.340
 


00:03:46.340 --> 00:03:50.080
'Nadi Shuddhi' will
occur naturally.

00:03:50.080 --> 00:03:54.320
Always change direction after exhaling. That is,


00:03:54.320 --> 00:03:56.480
 
after inhaling,

00:03:56.480 --> 00:04:01.360
 
exhale through the nostril on the same side. Continue

00:04:01.360 --> 00:04:06.680
'Nadi Shuddhi' for
at least 4 minutes. Let me give you

00:04:07.900 --> 00:04:10.620
a few points to note.


00:04:10.620 --> 00:04:14.210
 
Do not rest your left hand on your thigh; instead,

00:04:14.210 --> 00:04:18.980
 
place it comfortably in the center of your leg.

00:04:18.980 --> 00:04:20.430
In other words,

00:04:20.430 --> 00:04:24.580
 
use only your thumb and ring finger with your right hand.

00:04:24.580 --> 00:04:29.880
Extend your ring and little fingers so they
touch each other.

00:04:29.880 --> 00:04:33.480
Fold your index and middle fingers. If you cannot straighten your

00:04:33.480 --> 00:04:36.900
ring and little fingers,


00:04:36.900 --> 00:04:38.620
extend them as much as you can. Sometimes people

00:04:53.540 --> 00:04:55.850
 
lower their heads or

00:04:55.850 --> 00:05:01.080
 
tilt them to one side. Keep your head upright so that your face does

00:05:01.080 --> 00:05:06.140
 
not unconsciously tilt to one side. If you do

00:05:06.140 --> 00:05:09.320


00:05:09.320 --> 00:05:10.870
this,

00:05:10.870 --> 00:05:15.740
your system will
find balance very quickly.

00:05:15.740 --> 00:05:20.730
 
Do not press too hard on the area below the nostrils. If you gently press with your thumb slightly below where the bone

00:05:20.730 --> 00:05:23.910
of the right nostril
ends...

00:05:23.910 --> 00:05:27.520
 


00:05:27.520 --> 00:05:29.890
 
Completely block your nostrils so that

00:05:29.890 --> 00:05:34.620
 
no air leaks out.

00:05:34.620 --> 00:05:36.460
 


00:05:36.460 --> 00:05:38.640
 
Whether you breathe shallowly or normally,

00:05:38.640 --> 00:05:41.360
 
do not hold your breath.

00:05:41.360 --> 00:05:43.630
Breathe in
completely and breathe out

00:05:43.630 --> 00:05:47.140
completely.

00:05:47.140 --> 00:05:51.560
Now, let's try 'Nadi Shuddhi'
together. Sit with your

00:05:54.620 --> 00:05:57.820
legs comfortably
folded.

00:05:57.820 --> 00:06:00.320
 
Keep your spine upright and relaxed. If you cannot sit on

00:06:00.320 --> 00:06:01.790
the floor,


00:06:01.790 --> 00:06:06.630
sit on a chair and
cross your ankles. Place your

00:06:08.510 --> 00:06:11.850
left hand loosely and comfortably on your leg with your palm
facing up.

00:06:11.850 --> 00:06:15.920
 


00:06:15.920 --> 00:06:18.340
Use only your right hand. Use your

00:06:18.340 --> 00:06:20.900
thumb and ring finger, and


00:06:20.900 --> 00:06:24.230
 
fold your index and middle fingers. Extend your

00:06:24.230 --> 00:06:26.290
ring and
little fingers and

00:06:26.290 --> 00:06:29.990
 
bring their sides together.

00:06:29.990 --> 00:06:32.700
Close your eyes.

00:06:32.700 --> 00:06:36.280
Close your eyes.
 
Now, block your right nostril with your thumb and


00:06:36.280 --> 00:06:39.630
close your eyes.
 
 
Inhale through your left nostril.

00:06:39.630 --> 00:06:42.110
Close your eyes. Once you have
 
fully inhaled,


00:06:42.110 --> 00:06:46.420
close your eyes.
 
 
Exhale through the nostril on the same side.

00:06:46.420 --> 00:06:49.440
Close your eyes.
 
Now,
block your left nostril with your ring finger and close your

00:06:49.440 --> 00:06:54.690
eyes.
 
Open your right nostril and inhale.


00:06:54.690 --> 00:07:00.540
Close your eyes.
 
Then
exhale to the same side.

00:07:00.540 --> 00:07:06.780
Close your eyes.
 
Again, block the right side and
open the left to inhale.

00:07:06.780 --> 00:07:09.910
Close your eyes.
 
 
Then exhale.

00:07:09.910 --> 00:07:14.570
Close your eyes.
 
This breath
Continue until told to stop.

00:07:14.570 --> 00:07:15.700
Close your eyes.

00:07:15.700 --> 00:07:19.150
Close your eyes.
 
 
Focus on your breath.

00:07:19.150 --> 00:07:22.300
Close your eyes.

00:07:22.300 --> 00:07:27.460
Close your eyes. Breathe in
 
completely and
breathe out completely. Close your eyes.

00:07:27.460 --> 00:07:31.300
 
 
 
Do it as slowly and quietly as you can.

00:07:31.300 --> 00:07:48.700
Close your eyes.

00:07:48.700 --> 00:07:51.490
Close your eyes. Keep your
 
spine
relaxed but straight, and

00:07:51.490 --> 00:08:03.360
close your eyes.

00:08:03.360 --> 00:08:05.700
Close your eyes. Keep your head
 
 
upright.

00:08:05.700 --> 00:08:17.150
Close your eyes.

00:08:17.150 --> 00:08:19.520
Close your eyes.
 
 
Continue to focus on your breath.

00:08:19.520 --> 00:09:52.040
Close your eyes.

00:09:52.060 --> 00:09:55.420
Close your eyes.
 
 
End your breath by exhaling to the left.

00:09:55.420 --> 00:10:03.140
Close your eyes.

00:10:03.140 --> 00:10:04.960
Slowly open your eyes.

00:10:09.230 --> 00:10:11.890
Peace is
not the ultimate goal of life.

00:10:11.890 --> 00:10:15.280
Peace is the
most fundamental necessity in life.

00:10:15.280 --> 00:10:18.270
 
If you make peace the ultimate goal of life, you will be able to rest peacefully

00:10:18.270 --> 00:10:22.730
only in death.


